==Entrances and Exits==
===Entrances===
*Finding a door in [[Level 59]] that leads to an emergency staircase will bring one to '''Level 58'''.
*There are rumors that sleeping at [[Level 19]] will bring one to '''Level 58''', but this remains only a theory.
*Staying in dark areas for an extended period at [[Level 15]] may cause one to pass out and wake up in '''Level 58'''.
===Exits===
*Entering a random door that appears to lead to daylight may lead one to [[Level 69]].
*Level 58 may fade into [[Level 73]] if one waits in it long enough.
*Entering one of the random doors located on the walls may result in a trip to [[The Void]].

